Watching the movie "Independence Day" and Judd Hirsch looks at Jeff Goldblum and says, "I'm proud of you son."  It made me think how many times I've said that to my sons.  Not nearly enough.  I think I need to change that.    If you want to be free, there is but one way; it is to guarantee an equally full measure of liberty to all your neighbors. There is no other. Carl Schurz